e an item with constant effect chamleon or invis at 100 magnitude then as long as you don't take an action *None* of the monsters will attack you.  Though you'll need to unequip it to talk to people.<br><br>That's some of the cheap and dirty tactics I've found in my playing hehehe what else have you guys found? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/upontiusont.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pontiusont</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/26/02 5:13:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> Was wanting to try this but I keep forgetting...<br><br>If you nuke a monster when your high up in the sky, is there a way for them to hit ya? Cause if not you could make a constant effect levitate item and just rain firebolts from the sky all day hehe <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Board Mistress</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/26/02 11:28:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.one.se/users/chribesk/edeina.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Yep, Pontiusont, that works.<br>As long as you are outdoors and the enemy can't cast spells or use ranged weapons. Then again, such monsters rarely give any loot to speak of. And killing mobs don't give XP in this game.<br><br>I have been toying around a bit with Chamelon, and it's more vicious then Sariah describe. Invisibility is alwasy 100% but breaks if you open a door, cast a spell, use a weapon, or similar. Chamelon is a percentage, and no item can hold 100%. But it doesn't break no matter what I do. And like Sariah said, multiple items are stackable. So far I havn't met a mob or NPC that can hit me back, melee or spells. Going to try it on the god Vivec now I think. <p>Love, Edeina<br>Retired Highelf Arch Mage of Erollisi.<br>Citizen of <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero">Ayonae Ro</a>, member of <a href="http://www.eternalwrath.org">Eternal Wrath</a>.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Board Mistress</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/26/02 11:58:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.one.se/users/chribesk/edeina.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Hrmf.<br>Vivec handed my ass to me.<br>Guess he see invis or something. <p>Love, Edeina<br>Retired Highelf Arch Mage of Erollisi.<br>Citizen of <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero">Ayonae Ro</a>, member of <a href="http://www.eternalwrath.org">Eternal Wrath</a>.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usairahlilhealer.showP