 your ability adds say 25 points of sanctuary then monsters attacking your characters have a 25% chance of completely missing.<br><br>Sanctuary effects from different items and spells do stack meaning it's possible to gain 100 points of sanctuary, meaning monsters have 100% chance of missing you with a melee attack.  Which means your character is invuln to being hit from melee because every attack would have 100% chance to miss.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=46.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=46.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=46.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.threadControl?topicID=46.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=46.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=46.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub42.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cells